            . I was walking along by <placeName id="t17670429-8-crimeloc34">the Change</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17670429-8-crimeloc34" type="placeName" value="the Change"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17670429-8-crimeloc34" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17670429-8-off32 t17670429-8-crimeloc34"></join>, on Saturday the 4th instant, about one o'clock at noon; a man came and told me my pocket was picked; I felt and missed my handkerchief; he went and brought Claxton to me; he bid me take hold of him, and he would go and fetch the other; I took him into an apothecary's shop; he brought me two-more, but one of them was discharged; my handkerchief was found under Claxton, in the shop.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17670429-8-person90">
                  William 
                  Goodwin 
               <interp inst="t17670429-8-person90" type="surname" value="Goodwin"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17670429-8-person90" type="given" value="William"></interp>
